  <div class="chapter-hero"><div class="chapter-tag">Chapter 08</div><h1>Sessions</h1><p class="lead">Single-farmer, single-asset agri-tech service operations (Power Africa Kilikawi). Every session records planned vs. actual parameters side by side.</p></div>
  <div class="doc-body">
    <h2 class="section-h2">8.1 Session Detail Page</h2>
    <p>Divided into a left panel and a right Location map. Three cards on the left:</p>
    <div class="field-list">
      <div class="field-item"><div class="field-name">Session Summary (dark green)</div><div class="field-desc">Confirmed actual outcomes: Batteries Used, Duration (start–end time), Location (GPS coordinates), Total Actual Weight, Total Actual Cost (with trend indicator vs. estimated), M-Pesa Reference (primary payment evidence)</div></div>
      <div class="field-item"><div class="field-name">Estimated Session Details</div><div class="field-desc">Planned parameters: Activity Type, Date, Start Time, Estimated Weight, Estimated Cost per unit, Total Estimated Cost, Farmer Name, Location, Hub Station</div></div>
      <div class="field-item"><div class="field-name">Asset Details</div><div class="field-desc">Asset type and ID, Safety Checklist score (clickable), assigned battery ID</div></div>
    </div>

<figure class="doc-screenshot">
  <img src="img/page026_img066.jpeg" alt="Session detail — dark green Session Summary (actual), Estimated Session Details, and Asset Details" loading="lazy">
  <figcaption>Session detail — dark green Session Summary (actual), Estimated Session Details, and Asset Details</figcaption>
</figure>


<figure class="doc-screenshot">
  <img src="img/page027_img069.jpeg" alt="Session detail — agent info, M-Pesa reference, and location map" loading="lazy">
  <figcaption>Session detail — agent info, M-Pesa reference, and location map</figcaption>
</figure>

    <h2 class="section-h2">8.2 Creating a Session — 3-Step Wizard</h2>
    <div class="step-list">
      <div class="step-item"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-body"><strong>Schedule Session</strong> — Farmer selection, farm location (registered or manual lat/long for unregistered farms), hub station, date, start time. Activity type dropdown with dynamic fields per activity. <em>Session completed?</em> toggle allows back-entry of impromptu sessions without the full mobile flow.</div></div>
      <div class="step-item"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-body"><strong>Assign Asset and Agent</strong> — Hub station confirmed; agent selected from available agents at that hub; asset selected from the pool matching the activity type (e.g. selecting Milling shows only Millers).</div></div>
      <div class="step-item"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-body"><strong>Associate Batteries (Optional)</strong> — Selected from available batteries at the hub. Battery assignment is optional at creation but mandatory before execution.</div></div>
    </div>
    <h3 class="section-h3">Activity-Specific Fields</h3>
    <table class="doc-table">
      <tr><th>Activity Type</th><th>Estimated Parameters</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Tilling / Ploughing</td><td>Estimated Area (sq.m), Estimated Cost per sq.m, Total Estimated Cost</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Milling / Grinding / Threshing / Chaff Cutting</td><td>Estimated Weight (kg), Estimated Cost per kg, Total Estimated Cost</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Water Pumping</td><td>Estimated Volume (litres), Estimated Cost per litre, Total Estimated Cost</td></tr>
    </table>
    <h2 class="section-h2">8.3 Session Flow Overview</h2>
    <div class="flow">
      <div class="flow-step">Farmer dials *384*385#</div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step">Request created (Pending)</div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step teal">Hub Manager accepts</div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step">SMS to farmer</div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step">Agent completes session on mobile</div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step teal">Actual vs. Estimated recorded</div>
    </div>

<figure class="doc-screenshot doc-screenshot-wide">
  <img src="img/page029_img074.png" alt="Sessions flow at a glance — end-to-end flow from USSD dial to actual vs. estimated recording" loading="lazy">
